# Project Documentation

## 1. Project Overview

### Directory Structure
The project follows a standard Django backend and React (Vite) frontend structure.

- **Backend**: Django Project (`company-website`)
    - **Apps**:
        - `projects`: Manages project portfolio data.
        - `services`: Handles services and technology listings.
        - `about`: About Us information.
        - `contact`: Contact form submissions.
        - `estimation`: Project cost estimation logic.
        - `config_api`: Site configuration.
        - `cart`: Shopping cart functionality.
        - `chatbot`: Chatbot integration.
    - **Core**: Shared utilities, permissions, and responses.

- **Frontend**: React (Vite)
    - **API Layer**: Centralized API calls in `src/api/`.
    - **Components**: Reusable UI components grouped by feature.
    - **Pages**: Main route views (Home, About, Services, Projects, etc.).

## 2. API Documentation

### Base URL: `/api/`

### Authentication
- `POST /api/token/` - Obtain Token pair (Login)
- `POST /api/token/refresh/` - Refresh Token

### Projects
- `GET /api/projects/` - List all projects
- `POST /api/projects/` - Create a new project
- `GET /api/projects/{id}/` - Retrieve project details
- `PUT /api/projects/{id}/` - Update project (full)
- `PATCH /api/projects/{id}/` - Update project (partial)
- `DELETE /api/projects/{id}/` - Delete project

### Services
- `GET /api/services/services/` - List Services
- `POST /api/services/services/` - Create Service
- `GET /api/services/services/{id}/` - Retrieve Service
- `PUT /api/services/services/{id}/` - Update Service
- `PATCH /api/services/services/{id}/` - Update Service (partial)
- `DELETE /api/services/services/{id}/` - Delete Service
- `GET /api/services/technologies/` - List Technologies
- `POST /api/services/technologies/` - Create Technology
- `GET /api/services/technologies/{id}/` - Retrieve Technology
- `PUT /api/services/technologies/{id}/` - Update Technology
- `PATCH /api/services/technologies/{id}/` - Update Technology (partial)
- `DELETE /api/services/technologies/{id}/` - Delete Technology

### Cart
- `GET /api/cart/` - List/Retrieve Cart
- `POST /api/cart/` - Create/Update Cart
- `GET /api/cart/{id}/` - Retrieve Cart Item
- `PUT /api/cart/{id}/` - Update Cart Item
- `PATCH /api/cart/{id}/` - Update Cart Item (partial)
- `DELETE /api/cart/{id}/` - Delete Cart Item

### About Us
- `GET /api/about/` - List About Info
- `POST /api/about/` - Create About Info
- `GET /api/about/{id}/` - Retrieve About Info
- `PUT /api/about/{id}/` - Update About Info
- `PATCH /api/about/{id}/` - Update About Info (partial)
- `DELETE /api/about/{id}/` - Delete About Info

### Estimation
- `POST /api/estimation/calculate/` - Calculate Estimate

### Chatbot
- `POST /api/chatbot/` - Send Message

### Configuration
- `GET /api/config/` - Get Site Config

### Contact
- `POST /api/contact/` - Submit Contact Form

## 3. Project Reports & Data Schema

### Project Model (`apps.projects.models`)
The system maintains a detailed registry of projects with the following data points available for reporting and display:

| Field | Type | Description |
|-------|------|-------------|
| **Title** | String | Name of the project |
| **Category** | String | Project category (e.g., Web Dev, Mobile App) |
| **Summary** | Text | Brief overview of the project |
| **Description** | Text | Detailed project description |
| **Image** | URL | Link to project cover image |
| **Tech Stack** | JSON/List | List of technologies used (e.g., ["React", "Django"]) |
| **Tags** | JSON/List | Associated tags for filtering |
| **Live URL** | URL | Link to the live project (optional) |
| **Created At** | DateTime | Timestamp of creation |

### Reporting Capabilities
Reports can be generated based on:
- **Project Categories**: Grouping projects by their type.
- **Technology Usage**: Analyzing frequently used tech stacks.
- **Timeline**: Listing projects by creation date.
